---
return Astro.redirect('/', 301);
const docs = [
  {
    href: '/docs/future-axes-plan',
    title: 'Future Axes Plan',
    desc: '앞으로의 작업을 작은 질문이 아니라 큰 축으로 묶는 진행 원칙 문서.',
  },
  {
    href: '/docs/context-strategy-plan',
    title: 'Context Strategy Plan',
    desc: 'tmux, cmux, Google AI Studio, git worktree를 어떻게 나눠 쓸지 정리한 도구 선택 문서.',
  },
  {
    href: '/docs/context-worktree-ops',
    title: 'Worktree Operations',
    desc: '컨텍스트가 찼을 때 실제로 worktree를 어떻게 분리하고 넘길지 정리한 운영 규칙 문서.',
  },
];

const quickStart = `# worktree 분리
git worktree add ../s-reborn-public codex/public-site
git worktree add ../s-reborn-admin codex/admin-recovery
git worktree add ../s-reborn-db codex/db-migration

# 확인
git worktree list

# 종료
git worktree remove ../s-reborn-public
git worktree remove ../s-reborn-admin
git worktree remove ../s-reborn-db
git worktree prune`;

const refCards = [
  {
    title: 'Hand-off',
    body: 'done / next / risks만 남기고 다음 worktree로 넘긴다.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Exit',
    body: 'commit → hand-off → remove → prune 순서로 닫는다.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Rebase',
    body: '충돌 시 중단 → 기준 선택 → 해소 → build → continue 순서로 처리한다.',
  },
];
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>S-Reborn Blog · 내부 문서</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #faf8f5;
      --surface: #fffdf9;
      --text: #1c1917;
      --muted: #5d564f;
      --accent: #8c6d45;
      --border: rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.12);
      --shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.06);
      --radius: 20px;
      --sans: 'Pretendard', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', sans-serif;
      --display: 'Paperlogy', 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--sans);
      color: var(--text);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fcfbf8 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
    }
    .wrap { width: min(960px, calc(100% - 2rem)); margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 0 4rem; }
    .hero, .card {
      background: rgba(255, 253, 249, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .hero { padding: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .eyebrow { color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    h1 { font-family: var(--display); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem); margin: 0.6rem 0 0.8rem; }
    .lede { color: var(--muted); margin: 0; max-width: 70ch; line-height: 1.7; }
    .grid { display: grid; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .card { padding: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block; }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); transition: transform 160ms ease; }
    .title { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 1.35rem; margin: 0 0 0.35rem; color: var(--text); }
    .desc { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }
    .link { margin-top: 0.8rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
    .quick {
      padding: 1.2rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: rgba(255, 253, 249, 0.92);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .quick-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .quick-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .quick-btn {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.85rem;
      font: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .quick-btn:hover { border-color: rgba(140, 109, 69, 0.35); }
    .ref-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .ref-card {
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 253, 249, 0.92);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .ref-title {
      margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-size: 1.02rem;
    }
    .ref-body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .quick-code {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(184, 149, 106, 0.2);
      background: #f6f1ea;
      color: #3f3529;
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow: auto;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
    }
    .footer { margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">S-Reborn Blog · Docs</div>
      <h1>컨텍스트 관리 문서</h1>
      <p class="lede">이 페이지는 작업 분리를 위한 기준 문서와 운영 문서를 모아둔 진입점입니다. 프로젝트 안에서 바로 열리고, GitHub에도 커밋 단위로 추적됩니다.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <section class="quick" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="quick-head">
          <h2 class="quick-title">Quick Start</h2>
          <button class="quick-btn" type="button" data-copy-worktree>복사</button>
        </div>
        <pre class="quick-code" data-worktree-snippet>{quickStart}</pre>
      </section>

      <section class="ref-grid" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        {refCards.map((card) => (
          <article class="ref-card">
            <h2 class="ref-title">{card.title}</h2>
            <p class="ref-body">{card.body}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </section>

      {docs.map((doc) => (
        <a class="card" href={doc.href}>
          <h2 class="title">{doc.title}</h2>
          <p class="desc">{doc.desc}</p>
          <div class="link">열기 →</div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </section>

    <p class="footer">직접 경로: <code>/docs/context-strategy-plan</code>, <code>/docs/context-worktree-ops</code></p>
  </main>

  <script>
    const button = document.querySelector('[data-copy-worktree]');
    const snippet = document.querySelector('[data-worktree-snippet]');
    if (button && snippet) {
      button.addEventListener('click', async () => {
        try {
          await navigator.clipboard.writeText(snippet.textContent || '');
          button.textContent = '복사됨';
          window.setTimeout(() => {
            button.textContent = '복사';
          }, 1200);
        } catch {
          button.textContent = '실패';
          window.setTimeout(() => {
            button.textContent = '복사';
          }, 1200);
        }
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
